attributes.title: We added tons of NEW guns to Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Prop Hunt and Murder are back in Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We've added Murder and Prop Hunt back into Gmod TTT! Time to sing that theme song!

attributes.title: The best update we've ever had in Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We added tons of guns and randomats but the best update we've ever had is in this episode of Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Even MORE new randomats! | Gmod TTT (Bonus Rounds!)
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We weren't able to see every new randomat in the last three episodes so we have some more bonus rounds of Gmod TTT for you!

attributes.title: This is the most confusing randomat we've ever had!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! This new randomat switches everyone's skins around and it's extremely confusing!

attributes.title: How does no one know their role?!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! This randomat removes the HUD and no one knows their role!!

attributes.title: NEW WEAPON - Hot Potato
attributes.description: Yes, that is Lewis' voice

attributes.title: Ravs has a UNIQUE gun that no one else can use?!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Someone coded in a unique gun for JUST RAVS to use and it's EXTREMELY overpowered in Gmod TTT!

attributes.description: This is the most confusing round of TTT we've ever played

attributes.description: So many plot twists

attributes.title: Zylus finds a new use for the Swapper
attributes.description: Such a troll

attributes.title: Don't let the swapper suck you
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Ben's a swapper. He's got the insta-kill suck suck gun.

attributes.title: This video is a 10 years old Christmas special
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We forgot to release this 10 year old video from our archives... Enjoy some 'ancient' Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Who would win? Three traitors or a glitch with a deagle?!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Who would win? Three professional traitors with access to the buy-menu or one dumb glitch with a deagle?

attributes.title: We're 1950s detectives, see!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! It was an episode like any other... 1 detective chasing after 2 traitors on the wrong side of the law. I sipped down my bourbon and--- you get the idea.

attributes.title: OPERATION: REZ BOBA
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We've recruited a lone hypnotist agent for the mission of a lifetime... Operation: Rez Boba!

attributes.title: We added a new role and immediately broke it
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We added the Old Man to Gmod TTT and we think we've already broken it... Whoops!

attributes.title: The ultimate Barnacle trap no one walked into
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! It turns out the hard counter to barnacles is just going to the beach in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Prop Hunt on this HUGE map was a mistake
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! This huge map has a ton of props so we made the mistake of trying out Prop Hunt in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Burp Cop Ben can kill from beyond the grave?!
attributes.description: Ben becomes the Burp Cop and possesses barrels to kill the traitors in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: The perfect counter to the Master of Stealth!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Ravs, the Master of Stealth, has a perfect counter now that we've changed the Romantic to the Revenger!

attributes.title: The most obvious traitors still end up winning
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We're really bad a listening, guys. They're obviously the traitors but we just didn't listen!

attributes.title: Boba gets hit by the dumbest traitor trap... twice!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! The traitors have found an incredible slow and easily avoidable trap in this map. Boba gets hit by it. Twice.

attributes.title: Ben gets naked and shows us how quick he is
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! If you carry less you run faster. If you're totally naked you run at super speed!

attributes.title: Buff Garfield will haunt Rythian forever
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Ravs has a brand new skin and it's gonna haunt Rythian for the rest of his days in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: We're farming innocent wins and ruining all your stats
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! This map has an innocent-win side-quest that is super easy to complete... so we're gonna farm it and ruin all your stats!

attributes.title: We gave Ravs too much power!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Traitor Ravs' items won't show up until next round... but next round he's a Detective! He's got too much power!

attributes.title: This weapon was banned for a reason!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Ben somehow buys a weapon we banned a long time ago!

attributes.title: Have we finally achieved world peace?!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Everyone has SLAMs but everyone has Floppers! No one can kill anyone, world peace has been achieved in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: They're Getting Married!
attributes.description: It's a glorious day in TTT, we're having a wedding!

attributes.title: The cat always gets the bat
attributes.description: The cat with a bat is back... and she always gets her bat.

attributes.title: NEW GUN that fires a explosive barrels
attributes.description: We're playing with a new gun today and it fires explosive barrels!

attributes.title: Phantom is now the best role in Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We changed the Phantom and now it's the best role in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: You don't want to make Zylus angry!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Zylus and Ben have brand new buff skins! You don't want to make them angry, though...

attributes.title: We're outsmarting the most confusing randomat in Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! These randomats completely hide our roles... but it doesn't matter! We've played enough Gmod TTT to know everyone's lying voices!

attributes.title: We're balancing Gmod TTT by giving everyone unbalanced guns!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! If everyone has the most overpowered gun in Gmod TTT then NO ONE has the most powerful gun in Gmod TTT... right?!

attributes.title: Gmod TTT but nothing is real and it's all inside Lewis' head
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! It's okay, Lewis, you're safe with Nurse Sharky and Doctor Zylus inside Gmod TTT.

attributes.title: We combined two randomats to make a slippery hell
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! One randomat makes the map totally frictionless and the other pushes you any time you shoot! It's a slippery hell in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: We're ruining Boba's weird Borrower dreams
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Boba wants her own Borrowers. We're going to make sure she never has that dream again in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: We ditch our guns and try to talk it out in Gmod TTT
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! What if we just threw away our guns and tried to talk it out? Could we find the traitors then?

attributes.title: NEW WEAPON: Shark Trap
attributes.description: Haven't you always wanted a portable device that ejects a gigantic killer shark?

attributes.title: Earthquake in the explosive barrel room
attributes.description: We've got a new randomat event that causes an earthquake and a few of the guys find themselves in a room full of explosive barrels when it hits.

attributes.title: Let's Speedrun TTT
attributes.description: Today we're seeing how quickly we can finish a round of TTT. Check out Tiny Teams on Steam and grab yourself a bargain on games from small developers: https://yogsca.st/TinyTeams

attributes.title: We revisit the Jaffa Factory in Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT... or is it Minecraft Tekkit? We're revisiting the Jaffa Factory in this extremely faithful recreation map!

attributes.title: Zylus is SICK of these monolingual IDIOTS
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! It's 2021! Learn another language!

attributes.title: Lewis tries to exploit the new roles, fails miserably
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! If Lewis is the Veteran and kills the Phantom then he's the last innocent alive which gives him a damage boost. The perfect exploit! How could it go wrong?!

attributes.title: You wanted us to play THIS map again?!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Back by popular demand... it's the drill map! Why did you want us to play this one again!?

attributes.title: We blow up the button map with artillery cannons
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We're back in the most stressful map we've ever played in Gmod TTT... but this time we have ARTILLERY CANNONS!

attributes.title: Whoops! We destroyed our Office in Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Welcome to YogStudios! This episode is going to cost us so much money...

attributes.title: How many times did we swap in ONE round?!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! This has got to be one of the most confusing rounds of Gmod TTT yet... how many times did we swap?!

attributes.title: Tiny Bus of Death + Total Mayhem
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! The Tiny Bus of Death returns again but this time we've got total mayhem. That insta-kill bus now explodes!!

attributes.title: We want to play Gmod TTT with Snoop Dogg and Doge Cage
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We're definitely showing our age with this one...

attributes.title: We found a MASSIVE bug with the Jester in Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! This should never have been a Jester win... this is a massive bug in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Zombies are back with these brand new roles in Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We added two more roles to Gmod TTT: the Mad Scientist and the Paramedic! That means more ressing and THAT means Zombies are back in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: We created an action movie with this new randomat
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! It's time to do the time warp again... but in reverse! Everything is going slower and that means it's action movie time with this randomat in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: This is the slowest two minutes in Gmod TTT history
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Let's do the praw emiT again! This is the slowest two minutes in Gmod TTT history!

attributes.title: We stop playing Gmod TTT and rob a bank instead
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT... at least it used to be! Now it's a bank heist game where we're trying to summon satan!

attributes.title: NEW ROLE? Nope, Ben is just a good boy
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Ben is a good boy! You can't shoot a good boy.

attributes.title: Don't play "dodge the bullets" with Pedguin!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We invent a new game and you really shouldn't play it with Pedguin. He's bad at these kinds of games.

attributes.title: FIVE traitors in ONE round?! HOW?
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! A randomat, a beggar and a glitch give us 5 traitors in one round of Gmod TTT!?

attributes.title: Boba unlocks 100% of her brain
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Turns out if we all talk in slow motion we can trick Boba into using 100% of her brain!

attributes.title: Zoey is TERRIFIED of the new zombies!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Zoey is the last one alive against a horde of zombies in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: This NEW DETECTIVE can see ghosts!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! We added some new detective roles including the Medium who can see ghosts of dead players in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: We investigate a haunted elevator and regret it immediately
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! This map has a haunted elevator that we, despite knowing exactly what will happen, decide to investigate!

attributes.title: This Traitor has EVERY WEAPON in Gmod TTT!?
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Lewis is somehow holding every traitor weapon available in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Would YOU buy a Zylus body pillow!?
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Just imagine Zylus wishing you a good night every night. What a dream...

attributes.title: Boba's Big Day Out (by Lewis Brindley)
attributes.description: Lewis wrote a short story for Boba that can only be told in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: We roleplay as cowboys for 15 straight minutes
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! You're either going to love or hate this episode because we're roleplayin' as cowboys today, yeehaw!

attributes.title: We added the Good Boy to Gmod TTT!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Remember when Ben was a Good Boy? Well today EVERYONE can be the Good Boy with this new role in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: We have way too much fun with boats in Gmod TTT
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! This is some of our best work in this incredible map that has some boats. We love those boats.

attributes.title: Is Ben the best Parasite we've had?!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! That's right, Ben is actually good as a Parasite in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: The worst horror movie tagline: Spooky This | Gmod TTT Halloween Special!
attributes.description: It's time for a spoOoOoky Gmod TTT and we're trying to find the traitor ghost in a haunted house! OoOoOoOoOoooo!

attributes.title: The server is fighting back and won't let us leave! | Gmod TTT
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! The server has turned evil and is forcing us to play this round of Gmod TTT forever... we can't get out!

attributes.title: We play limbo with a laser trip mine
A new kind of BARREL JUSTICE?!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Ravs finds a brand new kind of as-yet-unbanned Barrel Justice in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Who ya gonna call? BARNACLE BUSTERS!!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! If there's something strange on the roof right there... Who ya gonna call? Barnacle Busters!!

attributes.title: We didn't know these new roles existed!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! A randomat turns traitors into bees... but this time it's a NEW ROLE? When did that get added?!

attributes.title: "What is the Mud Scientist?"
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! Osie, our resident Gmod TTT noob, asks some fantastic questions sometimes like "what is a Mud Scientist?"

attributes.title: This is Ben's most BRUTAL experiment yet!
attributes.description: It's Gmod TTT! If we don't shoot then we start burning... but what if we're handcuffed?! I never agreed to this experiment in Gmod TTT!

attributes.title: Ravs pulls off a perfect impostor play
attributes.description: Ravs goes full on method actor when he manages to convince the team he's the detective when he's actually the traitor. BLACK FRIDAY SALE! Buy TTT hanging ornaments here: https://store.yogscast.com/products/ttt-hanging-ornaments

attributes.title: Balancing on the very top of the map
